## Family  

Sutherland married [Elizabeth Sutherland, 19th Countess of Sutherland](/Elizabeth_Leveson-Gower,_Duchess_of_Sutherland) on 4 September 1785. Their children were:  

* **[George Sutherland‑Leveson‑Gower, 2nd Duke of Sutherland](/George_Sutherland-Leveson-Gower,_2nd_Duke_of_Sutherland)** (1786–1861)  
* **Lady Charlotte Sophia Leveson‑Gower**, who became **[Charlotte Fitzalan‑Howard, Duchess of Norfolk](/Charlotte_Fitzalan-Howard,_Duchess_of_Norfolk)**  
* **Lady Elizabeth Mary Leveson‑Gower**, who married **[Richard Grosvenor, 2nd Marquess of Westminster](/Richard_Grosvenor,_2nd_Marquess_of_Westminster)**  
* **[Francis Leveson‑Gower, 1st Earl of Ellesmere](/Francis_Egerton,_1st_Earl_of_Ellesmere)** (1800–1857)  

The duchess survived her husband by six years, dying in January 1839. Both were buried at [Dornoch Cathedral](/Dornoch_Cathedral).  

